item.title: Tammy Baldwin biograph
item.description: Senator Tammy Baldwin Biograph Senator Tammy Suzanne Green Baldwin (D) is an American lawyer and politician. She has been serving as a junior U.S. Senator from Wisconsin under the Democrats since 2013. She was a member of the Wisconsin State Assembly from 1992 to 1998. She also served as a member of the U.S. House of Reps from 1999 to 2013. Baldwin was born in Madison, Wisconsin, on February 11, 1962.
